N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 16 ยง 665.3 - Commissions

State Regulations

Commissions paid to others or employees in place of
compensation or salaries for services rendered, for example, public telephone
commissions, shall be charged to the appropriate expense accounts and not to
the revenue accounts. Notes
